{"tid":2392128,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"七點封區，自我宵禁","createTime":"2021-02-02T15:22:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-03T00:26:11.000Z","uid":137789,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"18107d5c9f1c5c1143fed891ff10ac7546d339a8","tid":2392128,"uid":137789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T15:22:11.000Z","msg":"七點封區又唔知封邊，變咗個個要驚做緊嘢俾人封，情願唔做或者早啲做完返屋企，變相個個自我宵禁"},{"pid":"94ca339063951173f66b83d022a353c327c0267f","tid":2392128,"uid":137789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T15:23:31.000Z","msg":"深水埗有正在髮型屋染髮的市民遇著突襲封區，滿頭染料下獲安排排隊檢測。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2391801\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2391801</a>"},{"pid":"d74a63ba42e503e298b499746748cfcb0d1522b7","tid":2392128,"uid":137789,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T15:27:32.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">香港人而家正正係被再教育</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4女學生佐敦補習遇突擊封區　一度未能離開<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2392103\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2392103</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在佐敦長樂街「受限區域」內的百樂大廈，今晚（2日）有4名女學生在補習後放學時適逢突擊封區而未能離開。民政總署人員安排4人先行採樣本檢測，並要求她們聯絡家長到場接送。其中一名家長到場時表示，擔心女兒沒有足夠食物及行裝而要在補習社過夜。至晚上9時半過後，在民政總署安排及准許下，警員登記家長及學生資料後，安排他們離開封鎖區。"},{"pid":"b9793decefe994f7b39cb9f4ff86c5b7c57761ae","tid":2392128,"uid":137789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T15:32:47.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">今晚返風</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【政府幫緊你幫緊你　床墊都有埋】<br />\n<br />\n政府連日「突襲封區」，繼昨日封鎖四區後，今日（2 日）再在深水埗、佐敦及天水圍劃出「受限區域」。記者發現，在佐敦「受限區」政府準備的物資中，亦包括了床墊。<br />\n<br />\n昨日曾有「受限區」內的市民向傳媒抱怨，指自己只是路過，卻「無辜」被禁足，更沒有居所，要在檢測站附近借椅子過一晚。未知床墊是否為此準備。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3865313623554229/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F710476795704610%2Fposts%2F3865313623554229%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=FM8PVMPbIH5fyb1BVmxPrc22uFAamDTqma2v4g3iiws%3D&h=a3d39e9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3865313623554229/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n政府安排左床墊 可能俾封區內禁足既路過市民⋯⋯訓街<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2392139\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2392139</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7b5f6da73713d698bdc8ed21a72736c770f963b4","tid":2392128,"uid":137789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T15:51:02.000Z","msg":"俾GME洗晒版"},{"pid":"2ff14bc4466a1f2a35002cb18158b6daf23b5736","tid":2392128,"uid":137789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T16:16:55.000Z","msg":"沈旭暉：在新疆，嚴格監控最初都是以「安心」之名，讓當地人慢慢積非成是<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2392050\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2392050</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e41729fe9fe6e8f8893047e228144faa34d3a4fa","tid":2392128,"uid":83874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T22:47:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc1d34bb6b6ad922d7c9dbdaf2fa8fc4dba68979","tid":2392128,"uid":137789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e41729fe9fe6e8f8893047e228144faa34d3a4fa","tid":2392128,"uid":83874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T22:47:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T00:26:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}